[392.6, 491.4, 436.6, 514.4]}, {"text": "18", "bbox": [696.2, 493.2, 717.1, 516.3]}, {"text": "(a)", "bbox": [340.5, 523.3, 355.2, 535.3]}, {"text": "All of our barges are double-hulled.", "bbox": [378.0, 525.7, 616.7, 544.1]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2013, we owned 170 transport trucks and 161 trailers with an aggregate capacity of 1.5 million gallons for", "bbox": [96.6, 565.7, 1161.2, 588.8]}, {"text": "the movement of refined products and crude oil. In addition, we had 2,138 leased and 27 owned railcars of various sizes and", "bbox": [96.6, 590.7, 1138.1, 613.8]}, {"text": "capacities for movement and storage of refined products. The following table sets forth additional details about our railcars.", "bbox": [96.6, 615.7, 1127.3, 638.8]}, {"text": "Number of Railcars", "bbox": [561.2, 657.0, 737.2, 680.1]}, {"text": "Class of Equipment", "bbox": [245.6, 686.2, 420.5, 709.3]}, {"text": "Owned", "bbox": [515.0, 686.2, 578.7, 709.3]}, {"text": "Leased", "bbox": [617.8, 686.2, 680.3, 709.3]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [728.4, 686.2, 775.8, 709.3]}, {"text": "Capacity per Railcar", "bbox": [818.8, 686.2, 1005.3, 709.3]}, {"text": "General service tank cars", "bbox": [245.6, 715.6, 455.8, 738.7]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [566.0, 717.5, 586.8, 740.6]}, {"text": "763", "bbox": [657.7, 717.5, 689.0, 740.6]}, {"text": "763", "bbox": [759.8, 717.5, 791.1, 740.6]}, {"text": "20,000-30,000 gallons", "bbox": [812.7, 717.5, 999.7, 740.6]}, {"text": "High pressure tank cars", "bbox": [245.6, 746.9, 441.9, 769.9]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [566.0, 748.8, 586.8, 771.8]}, {"text": "1,166", "bbox": [642.0, 748.8, 689.0, 771.8]}, {"text": "1,166", "bbox": [744.2, 748.8, 791.1, 771.8]}, {"text": "33,500 gallons", "bbox": [812.7, 748.8, 935.5, 771.8]}, {"text": "Open-top hoppers", "bbox": [245.6, 778.1, 395.6, 801.2]}, {"text": "27", "bbox": [566.0, 780.0, 586.8, 803.1]}, {"text": "209", "bbox": [657.7, 780.0, 689.0, 803.1]}, {"text": "236", "bbox": [759.8, 780.0, 791.1, 803.1]}, {"text": "4,000 cubic feet", "bbox": [812.7, 780.0, 946.4, 803.1]}, {"text": "27", "bbox": [566.0, 811.3, 586.8, 834.3]}, {"text": "2,138", "bbox": [642.0, 811.3, 689.0, 834.3]}, {"text": "2,165", "bbox": [744.2, 811.3, 791.1, 834.3]}, {"text": "Speedway", "bbox": [96.6, 863.7, 185.8, 886.8]}, {"text": "Our Speedway segment sells gasoline and merchandise through convenience stores that it owns and operates, primarily under", "bbox": [96.6, 895.0, 1149.2, 918.1]}, {"text": "the Speedway brand. Diesel fuel is also sold at the vast majority of these convenience stores. Speedway-branded convenience", "bbox": [96.6, 920.0, 1149.1, 943.1]}, {"text": "stores offer a wide variety of merchandise, including prepared foods, beverages and non-food items. Speedway’s Speedy", "bbox": [96.6, 945.0, 1108.7, 968.1]}, {"text": "Rewards® loyalty program has been an industry-leading loyalty program since its inception in 2004, with a consistently", "bbox": [96.6, 970.0, 1103.7, 993.1]}, {"text": "growing base of more than 3.7 million active members. Due to Speedway’s ability to capture and analyze member-specific", "bbox": [96.6, 995.0, 1125.5, 1018.1]}, {"text": "transactional data, Speedway is able to offer the Speedy Rewards® members discounts and promotions specific to their buying", "bbox": [96.6, 1020.0, 1160.6, 1043.1]}, {"text": "behavior. We believe Speedy Rewards® is a key reason customers choose Speedway over competitors and it continues to drive", "bbox": [96.6, 1045.0, 1161.8, 1068.1]}, {"text": "significant value for both Speedway and our Speedy Rewards® members.", "bbox": [96.6, 1070.1, 713.4, 1093.1]}, {"text": "The demand for gasoline is seasonal, with the highest demand usually occurring during the summer driving season. Margins", "bbox": [96.6, 1113.8, 1138.3, 1136.9]}, {"text": "from the sale of merchandise tend to be less volatile than margins from the retail sale of gasoline and diesel fuel. The following", "bbox": [96.6, 1138.8, 1163.4, 1161.9]}, {"text": "table sets forth Speedway merchandise statistics for the past three years.", "bbox": [96.6, 1163.8, 698.1, 1186.9]}, {"text": "Speedway Merchandise Statistics", "bbox": [233.1, 1207.2, 528.4, 1230.3]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [697.0, 1207.2, 738.7, 1230.3]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [823.1, 1207.2, 864.8, 1230.3]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [949.5, 1207.2, 991.2, 1230.3]}, {"text": "Merchandise sales (in millions)", "bbox": [233.1, 1238.5, 495.4, 1261.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [664.7, 1238.5, 675.1, 1261.6]}, {"text": "3,135", "bbox": [712.9, 1238.5, 759.8, 1261.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [791.8, 1238.5, 802.3, 1261.6]}, {"text": "3,058", "bbox": [838.0, 1238.5, 884.9, 1261.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [916.9, 1238.5, 927.3, 1261.6]}, {"text": "2,924", "bbox": [965.2, 1238.5, 1012.1, 1261.6]}, {"text": "Merchandise gross margin (in millions)", "bbox": [233.1, 1269.8, 563.2, 1292.8]}, {"text": "825", "bbox": [728.6, 1269.8, 759.8, 1292.8]}, {"text": "795", "bbox": [853.6, 1269.8, 884.9, 1292.8]}, {"text": "719", "bbox": [980.8, 1269.8, 1012.1, 1292.8]}, {"text": "Merchandise as a percent of total gross margin", "bbox": [233.1, 1301.0, 622.8, 1324.1]}, {"text": "65%", "bbox": [739.0, 1301.0, 777.2, 1324.1]}, {"text": "67%", "bbox": [864.1, 1301.0, 902.3, 1324.1]}, {"text": "65%", "bbox": [991.2, 1301.0, 1029.5, 1324.1]}]}